Daly_City.Judah and 19th Avenue station: Judah and 19th Avenue is a light rail stop on the Muni Metro N Judah line, located in the Sunset District neighborhood of San Francisco, California where Judah Street crosses 19th Avenue (California Route 1). The station opened with the N Judah line on October 21, 1928. It has mini-high platforms for level boarding, making the stop handicapped accessible.
